<div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" n="1">
<div type="textpart" subtype="section" n="1">
<p>Et proficiscentes filii Israhel de Ramesse castra metati <lb/>
            sunt in Sochoth. <lb n="15"/>
            
</p>
          <p>Secunda mansio. in hac coquunt panes azymos et primum <lb/>
