            populus <choice><sic>ludaeorum</sic><corr>Iudaeorum</corr></choice> leprae sorde perfunditur nec redit ad <lb/>
            tabernaculum et pristinam recipit sanitatem, donec statutum plenitudinis <lb/>
            gentium tempus inpleat.</p></div>

