<div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" n="1">
<div type="textpart" subtype="section" n="1">
<p>Et profecti de <choice><sic>Hebrona</sic><corr>Hebro</corr></choice> castra metati sunt in <sic n="poss">Asion</sic> - <lb/>
            Gaber. 
</p>
          <p>Tricesima secunda mansio transfertur in 'ligna uiri' siue'dolationes <lb/>
