            Hebraeos <choice><sic>habotur</sic><corr>habetur</corr></choice>, Hihim-castra metati sunt in Dibon - Gad. 
</p>
          <p>Tricesima <sic>nonamansio</sic> interpretatur 'fortiter intellecta temptatio'. <lb/>
            pro hac in <choice n="0.00"><sic n="1">ordino</sic><corr n="766">ordine</corr></choice> historiae aliter scriptum repperi. postquam enim <lb/>
            castra metati sunt in Hieabarim in finibus Moab contra ortum solis, <lb n="5"/>
            legitur: inde <choice><sic>profccti</sic><corr>profecti</corr></choice> sunt et deuerterunt ad torrentem <lb/>
            <choice><sic>Zarcd</sic><corr>Zared</corr></choice>. et de hoc loco proficiscentes castra <choice><sic>mctati</sic><corr>metati</corr></choice> sunt <lb/>
            <sic>transArnon</sic>, quae est in solitudine finium Amorraei, eo <lb/>
            <sic>quodArnon</sic> in terminis sitMoabitarum et <sic>Amorracorum</sic>. <lb/>
</p></div>

<div type="textpart" subtype="section" n="2"><p>            et post haec uenerunt ad puteum, ubi cecinit Israhel carmen  <lb n="10"/>
            hoc: ascende, putee, quem foderunt principes et <choice><sic>apcruerunt</sic><corr>aperuerunt</corr></choice> <lb/>
