            <title type="sub">XCIII. (RESPONSUM SVNODI HIEROSOLVMITANAE AD SUPERIOREM THEOPHILI SVNODICAM EPISTULAM.)</title>
          </ab>
          <p>Domino et honorabili, beatissimo episcopo Theophilo Eulogius, <lb/>
            Iohannes et ceteri episcopi, qui Hierosolymis in sancta encaeniorum <lb/>
            die repperti sunt. 
</p>
<div type="textpart" subtype="section" n="1">
          <p>Nosti, domine cuncta laudabiliter pater, et ante nostras litteras, <lb/>
