<div type="textpart" subtype="section" n="2"><p>in eodem: exprobrauerunt mihi,  <lb/>
            qui tribulant me. pro quo uos inuenisse dixistis: <foreign xml:lang="grc">οἱ ἐχθροί μου</foreign>,<lb/>
