<div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" n="1">
<div type="textpart" subtype="section" n="1">
<p>Quinquagesimo quinto: quoniam multi bellantes <lb/>
            aduersum me, ab altitudine diei timebo. <lb/>
            et dicitis in Graeco uos inuenisse: <sic>nontimebo</sic>, quod <lb/>
            'additum est. et est ordo: 'quoniam multi dimicant aduersum me, <lb/>
            idcirco ego ab altitudine diei timebo', hoc est: 'non bellantes <lb n="5"/>
            aduersum me, sed tuum excelsum timebo lumen'.</p></div>

<div type="textpart" subtype="section" n="2"><p>in ipso: in ira  <lb/>
            <sic>popuos</sic> confringes. pro quo m Graeco legitur: <hi rend="italic"><sic>sv</sic> <sic>ogyy</sic><lb/>
