<div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" n="1">
<div type="textpart" subtype="section" n="1">
<p>Centesimo quarto decimo: et in diebus meis inuocabo <lb/>
            t e. dicitis, quod in Graeco non sit 'te', et bene; e uestris <lb/>
            quoque codicibus eradendum est.</p></div>

<div type="textpart" subtype="section" n="2"><p>m ipso: placebo domino  <lb/>
            <choice><sic>m</sic><corr>in</corr></choice> regione uiuorum. pro quo <choice><sic>m</sic><corr>in</corr></choice> <choice><sic>ijraeco</sic><corr>Graeco</corr></choice> legisse uos <sic>dlCltlS</sic>: <lb/>
            placebo in conspectu domini. sed hoc superfluum est. <lb n="5"/>
            
</p>
          
</div>
</div>
<div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" n="1">
<div type="textpart" subtype="section" n="1">
<p>Centesimo septimo decimo: et in nomine domini, <lb/>
            quia ultus sum ineos. dicitis 'quia' in Graecis codicibus <lb/>
            non inueniri; sed et in Latinis sub asterisco legendum est. 
</p>
          
</div>
</div>
