<p>Centesimo tricesimo octauo: <sic>quianonestsermoin</sic> <lb/>
            lingua <choice n="0.18"><sic n="4308">mea</sic><corr n="19088">me</corr></choice>. pro quo m Graeco legisse uos dicitis: <choice n="0.79"><sic n="36919">qui</sic><corr n="9788">quia</corr></choice> a non<lb n="10"/>
