<div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" n="1">
<div type="textpart" subtype="section" n="1">
<p>Centesimo tricesimo nono: funes extenderunt in <lb n="15"/>
            <sic n="poss">1aqueum</sic>. pro quo in Graeco inuenisse uos dicitis: <sic>funesextenderunt</sic> <lb/>
