<div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" n="1">
<div type="textpart" subtype="section" n="1">
<p>Adtende enim, obsecro, ipsa uerba Iacobi: uides, inquit, <lb/>
            frater, quot milia sunt in Iudaea, qui <lb/>
            crediderunt in Christum, et hi omnes aemulatores <lb/>
