<div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" n="1">
<div type="textpart" subtype="section" n="1">
<p>Dent ueniam quilibet aliud opinantes; ego magis credo <lb n="5"/>
            tanto apostolo in suis et pro suis litteris iuranti quam cuique <lb/>
